snippet.title: Amber Heard and Jimmy Take the Aquaman Spicy Bite Challenge
snippet.description:
After hearing about her spicy food challenge on the Aquaman set, Jimmy asks Amber Heard to eat increasingly spicy foods, including a thimble full of ghost pepper sauce, without taking a drink of milk or losing eye contact.
